the Blue Pump Room.

371
00:19:08,067 --> 00:19:10,667
In later iterations
it became the Old Abbey,

372
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,333
the Union Course Tavern,

373
00:19:12,367 --> 00:19:14,533
