00:30:24,733 --> 00:30:26,133
Like, one of
the best things about

591
00:30:26,167 --> 00:30:27,533
what happened right afterward

592
00:30:27,567 --> 00:30:29,721
was the way a lot of people
came together who lived here,

593
00:30:29,733 --> 00:30:31,700
but also how a lot of people
kind of came in,

594
00:30:31,733 --> 00:30:34,633
pitched in, brought food,
brought generators.

595
00:30:34,667 --> 00:30:38,133
